data.description:
Nestled in the serene neighborhood of Wapakoneta, discover the enchanting allure of 303 W. Mechanic Street. This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence beckons with its picturesque exterior and spacious, thoughtfully designed interior.
Upon entering, you're greeted by a large living room, providing an inviting space for gatherings. The first floor boasts a generously sized bedroom, complete with a big walk-in closet, offering both comfort and convenience. Adjacent to the bedroom, a remodeled bathroom showcases a magnificent clawfoot tub, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Additionally, the first floor laundry adds a touch of convenience to everyday chores!
Upstairs, two additional bedrooms and a bathroom provide ample space, ensuring everyone has their own private retreat.
The unfinished basement offers plenty of storage space, perfect for keeping belongings organized and out of sight.
Step outside to discover the enchanting outdoor spaces this property has to offer. A large covered front porch welcomes you to relax and enjoy the tranquility of the neighborhood, while out back, a spacious deck overlooking a large back yard provides the perfect spot for hanging out and entertaining!
For those with a passion for tinkering or DIY projects, the oversized 2-car garage is a dream come true, offering enough space for a workshop, complete with 200 amp service and wired 220. 
Don't miss your chance to make this charming residence your own. Schedule your showing today!
